---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'May 13, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Spark"
  description="How Spark collects, uses, and protects your information."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="legal">
    <article class="legal__inner">
      <p class="legal__eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="legal__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal__updated">Last updated {updated}</p>

      <p>
        Spark (“we,” “our,” or “us”) is built so people can meet each other for
        real connections. This policy explains what we collect, why, and the
        choices you have. We try to keep it short and plain.
      </p>

      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account info</strong> — name, date of birth, gender, email or phone, and the photos you upload.</li>
        <li><strong>Profile content</strong> — bio, prompts, “Hit Me Up” posts, chats, and love-note replies.</li>
        <li><strong>Location</strong> — city-level location to show you nearby people. You can disable precise location at any time in your device settings.</li>
        <li><strong>Device data</strong> — basic technical info (OS, app version, crash logs) so we can keep the app stable.</li>
        <li><strong>Payments</strong> — handled by Apple App Store and Google Play. We never see your card details.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How we use it</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To match you with compatible people and keep the experience safe.</li>
        <li>To moderate text and images for harassment, nudity, and underage content.</li>
        <li>To send you notifications you opted into (matches, messages, calls).</li>
        <li>To improve the product through aggregated, non-identifying analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Photo &amp; text moderation</h2>
      <p>
        Every photo you upload is checked by an automated moderator before it
        becomes visible to others. Profile photos are additionally checked for a
        clearly visible face. Every chat, comment, prompt, and love note is
        scanned for harmful content. We never share moderation reasons publicly.
      </p>

      <h2>Sharing</h2>
      <p>We don’t sell your data. We share only with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Service providers who run our infrastructure (hosting, push notifications, crash reporting), under contract.</li>
        <li>Law enforcement when required by valid legal process.</li>
        <li>People you choose to share with inside the app.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You can delete your account at any time from <strong>Settings → Account</strong>. This is permanent and removes your data.</li>
        <li>You can pause discovery, hide your distance, or block any user.</li>
        <li>You can opt out of marketing notifications while keeping match alerts.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children</h2>
      <p>
        Spark is strictly 18+. We use age-verification at signup and remove
        accounts that misrepresent age.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions or requests? Email <a href="mailto:privacy@sparkapp.dev">privacy@sparkapp.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
